  "id": "RAW_5e5b24",
  "title": "全网首测！ Qwen3 vs Deepseek-R1 数据分析哪家强？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/0kFACvGHnAjn_0kXwMDhhg",
  "date": "2025-04-30 05:11:25",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"421\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ZBjVrHIdkOlQfkZciaZDM5JFv32I98Eiaza4zyahRiaGMV1DyBGNtc0VIePicRbHLqryx3z4Yapf8WM1zvxW5A5Iow/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1280\" data-cropy2=\"608.9965397923876\" data-imgfileid=\"100125374\" data-ratio=\"0.4759259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7ee643cf-aba6-44d9-e99b-07975afba700/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7ee643cf-aba6-44d9-e99b-07975afba700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">作者 | 李飞 </span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">昨天凌晨，阿里巴巴开源新一代通义千问模型 Qwen3，AI Agent 厂商数势科技的数据分析智能体 SwiftAgent 已率先完成全面适配，并发布了 Qwen3 与 DeepSeek-R1 的测评报告，下面是具体评测内容，我们来看看在企业级的数据分析和智能决策场景上，Qwen3 与 DeepSeek-R1 到底有哪些差异？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">(声明: 本次测评主要针对 Qwen3-32B 和 Qwen3-235B-A22B, 对比 Qwen2.5-72B 和 R1 效果)</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对数据分析 Data Agent，我们有如下关键节点 (如图 1），分别是改写，任务编排，工具选择和参数解析，工具运行和总结等。其中数据查询工具又</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">涵盖了复杂的能力，例如如何将用户的查询语句解析成对应的语义层要素 (时间，指标</span><span leaf=\"\">，维度，逻辑算子等）。不同节点的准确性对最终结果都会造成较大的影响。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154814\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e33d5ba7-7e83-4d6a-0dfe-206ab2ccb800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e33d5ba7-7e83-4d6a-0dfe-206ab2ccb800/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图 1：数据分析 Agent 流程概要</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前在落地的过程中，不同厂商针对其中节点的准确性优化基本都是三种手段，分别是提示词工程、RAG 增强判断和模型微调等。这三种手段的实施成本是递进的，效果也不可控。因此，数势科技一直秉持积极拥抱最先进的开源大模型的原则，践行第一时间适配，以提高 Agent 产品的效果，降低交付中的实施成本。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">先说结论，在上下文改写、任务编排和工具调用、数据查询、图表生成、总结反思五个方面，Qwen3 对比 Qwen2.5 有极大的效果提升，对比 DeepSeek-R1 模型也不遑多让，甚至在某些环节上还有意外的惊喜。成本上，根据阿里官方的报告，Qwen3 模型在整体部署上成本极大地降低，进一步降低了各个企业部署和使用的门槛。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3194444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154815\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5fd4661d-c6fd-41f3-41c5-55849c98c800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5fd4661d-c6fd-41f3-41c5-55849c98c800/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">本次，数势科技的 SwiftAgent 产品针对其中的不同节点，对 Qwen3 大模型进行整体测评，并对比以往模型的效果。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc7e5f7e-5c25-43f0-297c-9c78ff41e100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">上下文改写</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Chat 类产品首先接收的就是用户的输入语句，由于会话通常存在上下文干扰，以及用户的输入往往都是非标准的，因此我们必须对用户当次的输入语句进行改写判断，符合“优质进，优质出”的原则。以下测试我们分别把上下文带入到大模型中进行改写，让大模型判断用户问题的语境并进行改写的判断。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154816\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c5fc334-997c-432c-175d-38c4df806200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c5fc334-997c-432c-175d-38c4df806200/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结：针对 Case1 的语境，不应该进行改写，出乎意料的只有 Qwen3-32B 回答准确；针对 Case2，由于本轮提问的语境是绝对时间，Qwen2.5-72B 会基于上轮时间进行推理，对本轮 Query 进行改写，其他模型则理解语境不会判断成改写。针对 Case3，INV 代表“当日库存量”的缩写，当大模型不理解该术语时，会擅自继承上轮内容并改写本轮 Query，4 个模型均没办法正确回答。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc7e5f7e-5c25-43f0-297c-9c78ff41e100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">任务编排和工具调用</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154818\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e7ed63b-e2eb-4ccd-fbbd-62166c868c00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e7ed63b-e2eb-4ccd-fbbd-62166c868c00/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Qwen2.5-72B 在数据分析任务拆解和工具调用选择上，均落后于其它三个模型</span>。其中，Case2 中我们期望通过子任务的拆解执行提高最终结果生成的准确性，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">DeepSeek-R1 以及 Qwen3-32B 和 Qwen3-235B-A22B 推理和非推理模式均表现优秀</span>，Qwen2.5-72B 无法成功拆解相应任务，Case3 中，Qwen2.5-72B 在第 5 步任务中无法识别到应该调用归因分析工具，其它三个模型均能做到。可见&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Qwen3-32B 做到了成本下降了，效果反而更好了</span>。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc7e5f7e-5c25-43f0-297c-9c78ff41e100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">数据查询</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据要素解析中，对时间要素的识别往往是较难的，因为时间是带动态更新和逻辑推理特性的。例如：“我行销售额较去年增加多少”是时间的隐性推理，实际表达的时间是“今年”和“去年”。此外还有相对时间和绝对时间理解，以及周的开始和结束时间推理识别等。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154819\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/857f2a9f-5b63-4b0b-ef80-72d841646b00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/857f2a9f-5b63-4b0b-ef80-72d841646b00/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">总结：在这三种时间难例 Case 下，DeepSeek-R1 以及 Qwen3-32B 和 Qwen3-235B-A22B 推理和非推理模式均领先于 Qwen2.5-72B，其中 Qwen3-32B 的效果已经完全接近 R1 的识别效果。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据要素解析中，对实体的抽取也是要素匹配的一个前提条件，实体抽取的质量好坏会干扰后面要素匹配的效果，针对以往的难例 case，不同模型的测试情况如下：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154821\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f3e61804-70d1-42e2-ab16-357ea42b9500/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f3e61804-70d1-42e2-ab16-357ea42b9500/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结：DeepSeek-R1 和 Qwen3-32B 在 Case1 和 Case2 的效果优于其他模型，然而 DeepSeek-R1 在 Case3 上漏识别了维度，总体来看，实体语义识别的效果差距不大，反而 Qwen3-32B 的 Dense 模型效果要优于其他模型。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc7e5f7e-5c25-43f0-297c-9c78ff41e100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">图表生成</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">本次评测中，我们采用 Echart 图表生成的方式来验证不同模型基于数据的理解后，生成并渲染图表的效果</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154822\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/69d94d5a-4cb1-47c4-a9bd-47f943b6dc00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/69d94d5a-4cb1-47c4-a9bd-47f943b6dc00/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结：Qwen72B 对于数据理解和代码生成的能力弱于 Qwen3-32B, Case2 和 Case3 中甚至出现了数据遗漏的现象。此外，Qwen3-32B 在渲染排版上略逊色于 Qwen3-235B-A22B 和 DeepSeek-R1 模型。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fc7e5f7e-5c25-43f0-297c-9c78ff41e100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">总结反思</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里，我们测试了针对生成的错误代码，大模型是否可以结合错误反思并生成准确的代码。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4861111111111111\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/598ef800-6570-4eea-dc96-2147a4f1eb00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/598ef800-6570-4eea-dc96-2147a4f1eb00/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结：原始代码存在包括</span><span leaf=\"\">【类型错误】</span><span leaf=\"\">、</span><span leaf=\"\">【潜在的空列表错误】</span><span leaf=\"\">、</span><span leaf=\"\">【字符串与整数操作问题】</span><span leaf=\"\">等数据分析中常见的代码问题。经过四个不同模型反思优化后，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Qwen2.5-72B</span>&nbsp;选择直接丢弃不符合数值格式的数据，虽然能够跑通，但<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">并不是数据预处理时的最佳选择</span>，优化了潜在的空列表错误。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">DeepSeek-R1&nbsp;</span>对数据进行了强制转换，但<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">传入无法强制转换的类型时，依旧会报错</span>，且并未解决潜在的空列表错误。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Qwen3 的两个模型对数据类型做了最符合预期地处理，优先尝试转换为数值，无法强制转换才选择抛弃</span>，但同样并未解决潜在的空列表错误。关于潜在的空列表错误，在二次提示优化后，四个模型均给出优化方案，达到预期。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，我们还测了一些其他和数据分析相关的大模型能力，例如数学推理计算能力，我们从网上借鉴了一些数学测试题，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">先说结论，DeepSeek-R1 模型和 Qwen3-235B-A22B 在数学计算推理能力上要优于另外两种模型，符合 Scale Law 的认知</span>。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100154823\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8b71497c-5922-489f-5483-77537a6c5700/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8b71497c-5922-489f-5483-77537a6c5700/public\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体来说，Case1 中，DeepSeek-R1 模型和 Qwen3-235B-A22B 均回答正确，其他两个模型回答错误。Case2 和 Case3 中所有模型均回答准确。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">综上所述，在数据分析 Agent 构建方面，Qwen3 模型的发布对于 Agent 的构建有极大的提升作用。无论是在任务规划、代码生成、数学计算和语义识别等方面，Qwen3 模型都表现较为出色，其中 Qwen3-32B 模型也远优于上一代模型，甚至<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">接近于 DeepSeek-R1 模型，且部署成本更低，消费级显卡即可实现推理自由，对企业使用大模型来说，是重大的利好</span>。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Qwen3 模型发布的首日，数势科技 SwiftAgent 率先完成了对 Qwen3 的全面适配，并对 Agent 的中间环节进行了能力升级和创新性功能开发，为企业客户构建 AI 驱动的数据分析和智能决策提供了更高性能、更低成本的智能产品。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 30px 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 